# A dataset with all output variables generated by the euosi package

This table contains all soil indicators and soil quality scores for the
euosi package

## Usage

``` r
osi_vars_output
```

## Format

An object of class `data.table` (inherits from `data.frame`) with 29
rows and 2 columns.

## Details

- code:

  The name of the output parameter

- parameter:

  A description of the output parameter
